value.0:
Current description is:

<CUSTOM14438><CUSTOM14422><CUSTOM14435>

What do you want to do?

This is just a very simple text editor and it shouldn't be too difficult to use. 

Instead of pressing keys on the keyboard to move the cursor, delete parts of the text,...  you have to select the matching dialog options.

To insert new text you have to select the chat line using the mouse, then enter the text and press enter. Finally select <CUSTOM19993>Insert<CUSTOM19990> to insert the new text at the cursor position.

The editor supports simple block operations like mark block, delete block, copy block and insert block.

To write colored text you can select <CUSTOM19996> and choose one of the pre-made color tags. Don't forget to end the color mode using the color-off tag.
